### 1. Health check
GET http://localhost:3000/health

###

### 2. Registrar evento CREATE
POST http://localhost:3000/events
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "source": "crud-esports",
  "entity": "tournament",
  "action": "CREATE",
  "title": "Torneo creado",
  "description": "Se creó el torneo League of Legends 2026",
  "payload": {
    "id": 1,
    "name": "League of Legends 2026"
  }
}

###

### 3. Registrar evento UPDATE
POST http://localhost:3000/events
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "source": "crud-esports",
  "entity": "tournament",
  "action": "UPDATE",
  "title": "Torneo actualizado",
  "description": "Se actualizó la fecha del torneo",
  "payload": {
    "id": 1,
    "name": "League of Legends 2026",
    "date": "2026-06-15"
  }
}

###

### 4. Registrar evento DELETE
POST http://localhost:3000/events
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "source": "crud-esports",
  "entity": "tournament",
  "action": "DELETE",
  "title": "Torneo eliminado",
  "description": "Se eliminó el torneo de prueba",
  "payload": {
    "id": 1,
    "name": "League of Legends 2026"
  }
}

###

### 5. Registrar evento QUERY
POST http://localhost:3000/events
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "source": "crud-esports",
  "entity": "tournament",
  "action": "QUERY",
  "title": "Consulta realizada",
  "description": "Se consultó la lista de torneos",
  "payload": {
    "filters": "none"
  }
}

###

### 6. Obtener todos los eventos
GET http://localhost:3000/events

###

### 7. Filtrar por source
GET http://localhost:3000/events/source/crud-esports

###

### 8. Filtrar por entity
GET http://localhost:3000/events/entity/tournament

###

### 9. Stats
GET http://localhost:3000/stats